ActBudget Implementation Act, 2019, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day After the Day on Which this Order is Made as the Day on Which Certain Provisions of that Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the day after the day on which this Order is made as the day on which subsections 163(2) and (4), section 166 and subsections 168(2), 172(2), (7) and (8), 173(2), 174(2) and 175(2) of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2019, NO. 1, chapter 29 of the Statutes of Canada, 2019, COME INTO FORCE.
